description:
Zac Thompson grew up in Prince Edward Island, Canada. Home to Anne of Green Gables. There he spent years writing Doctor Who fan-fiction when he should have been studying.

After a few years writing film, he moved on to journalism and fiction. Now he writes comic books, novels, and weird stuff for VICE.
